<h1>Citadel Calgary Real Estate and Homes for Sale</h1>
<p>Citadel is a well-known family-friendly neighbourhood in Northwest Calgary. It is well-kept all year round and features a variety of paths, parks, playgrounds, and recreational areas. Many of the properties in Citadel have spectacular mountain and valley views due to the local topography.</p>

<div>#idx-c-citadel#</div>

